'''iPhone 15''' and '''iPhone 15 Plus'''{{efn|Also called '''iPhone 15+''' for short}} are to be released products in the [[iPhone]] line of [[Smartphone|smartphones]] made by [[Apple Inc.|Apple]] which may be released sometime in between September 15, 2023 and October 7, 2023.<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |title=iPhone 15: Everything We Know |url=https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/iphone-15/ |access-date=2022-09-02 |website=MacRumors |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web |last=Livemint |date=2022-10-11 |title=iPhone 15: How a note to Apple Store employees may have leaked its launch date |url=https://www.livemint.com/technology/gadgets/iphone-15-how-a-note-to-apple-store-employees-may-have-leaked-its-launch-date-11665465018083.html |access-date=2022-10-11 |website=mint |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web |last=gargi.chaudhry |title=iPhone 15 launched date leaked? Here's what we know so far |url=https://newsable.asianetnews.com/gadget-technology/apple-iphone-15-launched-date-leaked-here-is-what-we-know-so-far-gcw-rjkvve |access-date=2022-10-11 |website=Asianet News Network Pvt Ltd |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web |title=Apple iPhone 15 launch date reportedly leaked by Apple Store employee |url=https://www.dnaindia.com/technology/report-apple-iphone-15-launch-date-reportedly-leaked-by-apple-store-employee-2991931 |access-date=2022-10-11 |website=DNA India |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web |date=2022-10-10 |title=iPhone 15 release date LEAKED? Just check this out |url=https://tech.hindustantimes.com/mobile/news/iphone-15-release-date-leaked-just-check-this-out-71665414549452.html |access-date=2022-10-11 |website=HT Tech |language=en}}</ref> These phones are to be released with [[iOS 17]], which is in the [[iOS]] line of software made by [[Apple Inc.|Apple]].

== Design ==

=== Dynamic Island ===
The Dynamic Island may likely come to the non-Pro iPhone 15's. However, the Dynamic Island may be changed to include the proximity sensor, instead of the proximity sensor being under the Dynamic Island.<ref>{{Cite web |title=iPhone 15 Dynamic Island to Include New Integrated Proximity Sensor |url=https://www.macrumors.com/2023/03/24/iphone-15-dynamic-island-proximity-sensor/ |access-date=2023-04-26 |website=MacRumors |language=en}}</ref>

== Specifications ==

=== Charging Port ===
The whole iPhone 15 lineup may be switching to USB-C because of the EU regulations.<ref>{{Cite news |last=Ashworth |first=Boone |title=Apple Says iPhones Will Finally Get USB-C Ports |language=en-US |work=Wired |url=https://www.wired.com/story/apple-says-iphones-will-finally-get-usb-c-ports/ |access-date=2023-04-20 |issn=1059-1028}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Hern |first=Alex |date=2022-10-26 |title=Apple to put USB-C connectors in iPhones to comply with EU rules |language=en-GB |work=The Guardian |url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2022/oct/26/iphone-usb-c-lightning-connectors-apple-eu-rules |access-date=2023-04-20 |issn=0261-3077}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Simon |first=Michael |title=Apple confirms future iPhones will switch from Lightning to USB-C |url=https://www.macworld.com/article/1362886/apple-confirms-future-iphones-will-switch-from-lightning-to-usb-c.html |access-date=2023-04-20 |website=Macworld |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple Will Switch iPhone to USB-C Because 'We Have No Choice' |url=https://www.pcmag.com/news/apple-will-switch-iphone-to-usb-c-because-we-have-no-choice |access-date=2023-04-20 |website=PCMAG |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-10-10 |title=Apple’s iPhone 15 might make the switch to USB-C: Report |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/technology/tech-news-technology/apples-next-year-products-might-make-the-switch-to-usb-c-report-8200489/ |access-date=2023-04-20 |website=The Indian Express |language=en}}</ref>

=== Prices ===

Hypothetical prices for iPhone 15 and iPhone 15 Plus are listed below:<ref>{{Cite web |author1=Sean Riley |date=2022-09-07 |title=iPhone 15: Everything we know so far |url=https://www.laptopmag.com/news/iphone-15-everything-we-know-so-far |access-date=2022-09-10 |website=LaptopMag |language=en}}</ref>

iPhone 15: $799

iPhone 15 Plus: $899

== Software ==

The iPhone 15 and the iPhone 15 Plus will include [[iOS 17]].

